name: bulbasaur
flavor_text_en: A strange seed was planted on its back at birth.The plant sprouts and grows with this POKéMON.

name: ivysaur
flavor_text_en: When the bulb on its back grows large, it appearsto lose the ability to stand on its hind legs.

name: venusaur
flavor_text_en: The plant blooms when it is absorbing solarenergy. It stays on the move to seek sunlight.

name: charmander
flavor_text_en: Obviously prefers hot places. When it rains, steamis said to spout from the tip of its tail.

name: charmeleon
flavor_text_en: When it swings its burning tail, it elevates thetemperature to unbearably high levels.

name: charizard
flavor_text_en: Spits fire that is hot enough to melt boulders.Known to cause forest fires unintentionally.

name: squirtle
flavor_text_en: After birth, its back swells and hardens into ashell. Powerfully sprays foam from its mouth.

name: wartortle
flavor_text_en: Often hides in water to stalk unwary prey. Forswimming fast, it moves its ears to maintain balance.

name: blastoise
flavor_text_en: A brutal POKéMON with pressurized water jets on itsshell. They are used for high speed tackles.

name: caterpie
flavor_text_en: Its short feet are tipped with suction pads that enable it to tirelessly climb slopes and walls.

name: metapod
flavor_text_en: This POKéMON is vulnerable to attack while itsshell is soft, exposing its weak and tender body.

name: butterfree
flavor_text_en: In battle, it flaps its wings at high speed torelease highly toxic dust into the air.

name: weedle
flavor_text_en: Often found in forests, eating leaves.It has a sharp venomous stinger on its head.

name: kakuna
flavor_text_en: Almost incapable of moving, this POKéMON can onlyharden its shell to protect itself from predators.

name: beedrill
flavor_text_en: It has three poisonous stingers on its forelegs and its tail. They are used to jab its enemy repeatedly.

name: pidgey
flavor_text_en: A common sight in forests and woods. It flaps itswings at ground level to kick up blinding sand.

name: pidgeotto
flavor_text_en: Very protective of its sprawling territorial area,this POKéMON will fiercely peck at any intruder.

name: pidgeot
flavor_text_en: When hunting, it skims the surface of water at highspeed to pick off unwary prey such as MAGIKARP.

name: rattata
flavor_text_en: Bites anything when it attacks. Small and veryquick, it is a common sight in many places.

name: raticate
flavor_text_en: It uses its whis­ kers to maintain its balance.It apparently slows down if they are cut off.

name: spearow
flavor_text_en: It flaps its small wings busily to fly. Using its beak, it searches in grass for prey.

name: fearow
flavor_text_en: With its huge and magnificent wings, it can keep aloftwithout ever having to land for rest.

name: ekans
flavor_text_en: Moves silently and stealthily. Eats the eggs ofbirds, such as PIDGEY and SPEAROW, whole.

name: arbok
flavor_text_en: It is rumored that the ferocious warning markingson its belly differ from area to area.

name: pikachu
flavor_text_en: When several of these POKéMON gather, theirelectricity could build and cause lightning storms.

name: raichu
flavor_text_en: Its long tail serves as a ground to protect itself from its own high-voltage power.

name: sandshrew
flavor_text_en: Burrows deep underground in arid locationsfar from water. It only emerges to hunt for food.

name: sandslash
flavor_text_en: Curls up into a spiny ball when threatened. Itcan roll while curled up to attack or escape.

name: nidoran-f
flavor_text_en: Although small, its venomous barbs render thisPOKéMON dangerous. The female has smaller horns.

name: nidorina
flavor_text_en: The female's horn develops slowly. Prefers physicalattacks such as clawing and biting.

name: nidoqueen
flavor_text_en: Its hard scales provide strong protection. Ituses its hefty bulk to execute powerful moves.

name: nidoran-m
flavor_text_en: Stiffens its ears to sense danger. The larger itshorns, the more powerful its secreted venom.

name: nidorino
flavor_text_en: An aggressive POKéMON that is quick to attack.The horn on its head secretes a powerful venom.

name: nidoking
flavor_text_en: It uses its powerful tail in battle to smash,constrict, then break the prey's bones.

name: clefairy
flavor_text_en: Its magical and cute appeal has many admirers.It is rare and found only in certain areas.

name: clefable
flavor_text_en: A timid fairy POKéMON that is rarely seen. Itwill run and hide the moment it senses people.

name: vulpix
flavor_text_en: At the time of birth, it has just one tail.The tail splits from its tip as it grows older.

name: ninetales
flavor_text_en: Very smart and very vengeful. Grabbing one ofits many tails could result in a 1000-year curse.

name: jigglypuff
flavor_text_en: When its huge eyes light up, it sings a mysteriouslysoothing melody that lulls its enemies to sleep.

name: wigglytuff
flavor_text_en: The body is soft and rubbery. When angered, it willsuck in air and inflate itself to an enormous size.

name: zubat
flavor_text_en: Forms colonies in perpetually dark places. Usesultrasonic waves to identify and approach targets.

name: golbat
flavor_text_en: Once it strikes, it will not stop draining energyfrom the victim even if it gets too heavy to fly.

name: oddish
flavor_text_en: During the day, it keeps its face buried in theground. At night, it wanders around sowing its seeds.

name: gloom
flavor_text_en: The fluid that oozes from its mouth isn't drool.It is a nectar that is used to attract prey.

name: vileplume
flavor_text_en: It has the world’s largest petals. With every step, the petals shake out heavy clouds of toxic pollen.

name: paras
flavor_text_en: Burrows to suck tree roots. The mushrooms on itsback grow by draw­ ing nutrients from the bug host.

name: parasect
flavor_text_en: A host-parasite pair in which the parasite mushroomhas taken over the host bug. Prefers damp places.

name: venonat
flavor_text_en: Lives in the shadows of tall trees where iteats insects. It is attracted by light at night.

name: venomoth
flavor_text_en: The dustlike scales covering its wings are color-coded to indicate the kinds of poison it has.

name: diglett
flavor_text_en: Lives about one yard underground where it feeds onplant roots. It sometimes appears above ground.

name: dugtrio
flavor_text_en: A team of DIGLETT triplets. It triggers hugeearthquakes by burrowing 60 miles underground.

name: meowth
flavor_text_en: It washes its face regularly to keep the coin on its forehead spotless. It doesn’t get along with Galarian Meowth.

name: persian
flavor_text_en: Although its fur has many admirers, it is tough toraise as a pet because of its fickle meanness.

name: psyduck
flavor_text_en: While lulling its enemies with its vacant look, thiswily POKéMON will use psychokinetic powers.

name: golduck
flavor_text_en: Often seen swim­ ming elegantly by lake shores. Itis often mistaken for the Japanese monster, Kappa.

name: mankey
flavor_text_en: Extremely quick to anger. It could be docile onemoment then thrashing away the next instant.

name: primeape
flavor_text_en: Always furious and tenacious to boot. It will notabandon chasing its quarry until it is caught.

name: growlithe
flavor_text_en: Very protective of its territory. It will bark andbite to repel intruders from its space.

name: arcanine
flavor_text_en: A POKéMON that has been admired since the pastfor its beauty. It runs agilely as if on wings.

name: poliwag
flavor_text_en: Its newly grown legs prevent it from running. Itappears to prefer swimming than trying to stand.

name: poliwhirl
flavor_text_en: Capable of living in or out of water. When outof water, it sweats to keep its body slimy.

name: poliwrath
flavor_text_en: An adept swimmer at both the front crawl and breaststroke. Easily overtakes the best human swimmers.

name: abra
flavor_text_en: Using its ability to read minds, it will identifyimpending danger and TELEPORT to safety.

name: kadabra
flavor_text_en: It emits special alpha waves from its body thatinduce headaches just by being close by.

name: alakazam
flavor_text_en: Its brain can out­ perform a super­ computer.Its intelligence quotient is said to be 5,000.

name: machop
flavor_text_en: Loves to build its muscles. It trains in allstyles of martial arts to become even stronger.

name: machoke
flavor_text_en: Its muscular body is so powerful, it must wear a powersave belt to be able to regulate its motions.

name: machamp
flavor_text_en: Using its heavy muscles, it throws powerful punchesthat can send the victim clear over the horizon.

name: bellsprout
flavor_text_en: A carnivorous POKéMON that traps and eats bugs.It uses its root feet to soak up needed moisture.

name: weepinbell
flavor_text_en: It spits out POISONPOWDER to immobilize theenemy and then finishes it with a spray of ACID.

name: victreebel
flavor_text_en: Said to live in huge colonies deep in jungles,although no one has ever returned from there.

name: tentacool
flavor_text_en: Drifts in shallow seas. Anglers who hook them byaccident are often punished by its stinging acid.

name: tentacruel
flavor_text_en: The tentacles are normally kept short. On hunts,they are extended to ensnare and immobilize prey.

name: geodude
flavor_text_en: Found in fields and mountains. Mistaking themfor boulders, people often step or trip on them.

name: graveler
flavor_text_en: Rolls down slopes to move. It rolls over any obstaclewithout slowing or changing its direction.

name: golem
flavor_text_en: Its boulder-like body is extremely hard. It caneasily withstand dynamite blasts without damage.

name: ponyta
flavor_text_en: Its hooves are 10 times harder than diamonds. It cantrample anything completely flat in little time.

name: rapidash
flavor_text_en: Very competitive, this POKéMON will chase anythingthat moves fast in the hopes of racing it.

name: slowpoke
flavor_text_en: Incredibly slow and dopey. It takes 5 secondsfor it to feel pain when under attack.

name: slowbro
flavor_text_en: The SHELLDER that is latched onto SLOWPOKE's tailis said to feed on the host's left over scraps.

name: magnemite
flavor_text_en: Uses anti-gravity to stay suspended. Appears withoutwarning and uses THUNDER WAVE and similar moves.

name: magneton
flavor_text_en: Formed by several MAGNEMITEs linked together. Theyfrequently appear when sunspots flare up.

name: farfetchd
flavor_text_en: The sprig of green onions it holds is itsweapon. It is used much like a metal sword.

name: doduo
flavor_text_en: A bird that makes up for its poor flying with itsfast foot speed. Leaves giant footprints.

name: dodrio
flavor_text_en: Uses its three brains to execute complex plans.While two heads sleep, one head stays awake.

name: seel
flavor_text_en: The protruding horn on its head is very hard.It is used for bashing through thick ice.

name: dewgong
flavor_text_en: Stores thermal energy in its body. Swims at asteady 8 knots even in intensely cold waters.

name: grimer
flavor_text_en: Appears in filthy areas. Thrives by sucking uppolluted sludge that is pumped out of factories.

name: muk
flavor_text_en: Thickly covered with a filthy, vile sludge. Itis so toxic, even its footprints contain poison.

name: shellder
flavor_text_en: Its hard shell repels any kind of attack.It is vulnerable only when its shell is open.

name: cloyster
flavor_text_en: When attacked, it launches its horns in quickvolleys. Its innards have never been seen.

name: gastly
flavor_text_en: Almost invisible, this gaseous POKéMON cloaksthe target and puts it to sleep without notice.

name: haunter
flavor_text_en: Because of its ability to slip through blockwalls, it is said to be from an­ other dimension.

name: gengar
flavor_text_en: Under a full moon, this POKéMON likes to mimicthe shadows of people and laugh at their fright.

name: onix
flavor_text_en: As it grows, the stone portions of its body hardento become similar to a diamond, but colored black.

name: drowzee
flavor_text_en: Puts enemies to sleep then eats their dreams.Occasionally gets sick from eating bad dreams.

name: hypno
flavor_text_en: When it locks eyes with an enemy, it will use a mix ofPSI moves such as HYPNOSIS and CONFUSION.

name: krabby
flavor_text_en: Its pincers are not only powerful weapons, they areused for balance when walking sideways.

name: kingler
flavor_text_en: The large pincer has 10000 hp of crushing power.However, its huge size makes it unwieldy to use.

name: voltorb
flavor_text_en: Usually found in power plants. Easily mistakenfor a POKé BALL, they have zapped many people.

name: electrode
flavor_text_en: It stores electric energy under very high pressure.It often explodes with little or no provocation.

name: exeggcute
flavor_text_en: Often mistaken for eggs. When disturbed,they quickly gather and attack in swarms.

name: exeggutor
flavor_text_en: Legend has it that on rare occasions, one of its headswill drop off and continue on as an EXEGGCUTE.

name: cubone
flavor_text_en: Because it never removes its skull helmet, no onehas ever seen this POKéMON's real face.

name: marowak
flavor_text_en: The bone it holds is its key weapon. It throws thebone skillfully like a boomerang to KO targets.

name: hitmonlee
flavor_text_en: When in a hurry, its legs lengthen progressively.It runs smoothly with extra long, loping strides.

name: hitmonchan
flavor_text_en: While apparently doing nothing, it fires punches inlightning fast volleys that are impossible to see.

name: lickitung
flavor_text_en: Its tongue can be extended like a chameleon's. Itleaves a tingling sensation when it licks enemies.

name: koffing
flavor_text_en: Because it stores several kinds of toxic gases inits body, it is prone to exploding without warning.

name: weezing
flavor_text_en: Where two kinds of poison gases meet, 2 KOFFINGscan fuse into a WEEZING over many years.

name: rhyhorn
flavor_text_en: A POKéMON with a one-track mind. Once it charges, it won't stop running until it falls asleep.

name: rhydon
flavor_text_en: Protected by an armor-like hide, it is capable ofliving in molten lava of 3,600 degrees.

name: chansey
flavor_text_en: A rare and elusive POKéMON that is said to bringhappiness to those who manage to get it.

name: tangela
flavor_text_en: The whole body is swathed with wide vines that aresimilar to sea­ weed. Its vines shake as it walks.

name: kangaskhan
flavor_text_en: The infant rarely ventures out of its mother'sprotective pouch until it is 3 years old.

name: horsea
flavor_text_en: Known to shoot down flying bugs with precisionblasts of ink from the surface of the water.

name: seadra
flavor_text_en: Capable of swim­ ming backwards by rapidly flappingits wing-like pectoral fins and stout tail.

name: goldeen
flavor_text_en: Its tail fin billows like an elegant ballroomdress, giving it the nickname of the Water Queen.

name: seaking
flavor_text_en: In the autumn spawning season, they can be seen swimming powerfully up rivers and creeks.

name: staryu
flavor_text_en: If its body is torn, it can grow back if the red core remains. The core flashes at midnight.

name: starmie
flavor_text_en: Its central core glows with the seven colors ofthe rainbow. Some people value the core as a gem.

name: mr-mime
flavor_text_en: If interrupted while it is miming, it willslap around the offender with its broad hands.

name: scyther
flavor_text_en: With ninja-like agility and speed, it can create theillusion that there is more than one.

name: jynx
flavor_text_en: It seductively wiggles its hips as it walks. Itcan cause people to dance in unison with it.

name: electabuzz
flavor_text_en: Normally found near power plants, they can wanderaway and cause major blackouts in cities.

name: magmar
flavor_text_en: Its body always burns with an orange glow thatenables it to hide perfectly among flames.

name: pinsir
flavor_text_en: If it fails to crush the victim in its pincers,it will swing it around and toss it hard.

name: tauros
flavor_text_en: When it targets an enemy, it charges furiouslywhile whipping its body with its long tails.

name: magikarp
flavor_text_en: In the distant past, it was somewhat strongerthan the horribly weak descendants that exist today.

name: gyarados
flavor_text_en: Once it begins to rampage, a GYARADOS will burn everything down, even in a harsh storm.

name: lapras
flavor_text_en: A POKéMON that has been over­ hunted almost toextinction. It can ferry people across the water.

name: ditto
flavor_text_en: Capable of copying an enemy's genetic code to instantlytransform itself into a duplicate of the enemy.

name: eevee
flavor_text_en: Its genetic code is irregular. It may mutate ifit is exposed to radiation from element STONEs.

name: vaporeon
flavor_text_en: Lives close to water. Its long tail is ridgedwith a fin which is often mistaken for a mermaid's.

name: jolteon
flavor_text_en: It accumulates negative ions in the atmosphere toblast out 10000- volt lightning bolts.

name: flareon
flavor_text_en: When storing thermal energy in its body, itstemperature could soar to over 1600 degrees.

name: porygon
flavor_text_en: A POKéMON that consists entirely of programmingcode. Capable of moving freely in cyberspace.

name: omanyte
flavor_text_en: Although long extinct, in rare cases, it can begenetically resurrected from fossils.

name: omastar
flavor_text_en: A prehistoric POKéMON that died out when itsheavy shell made it impossible to catch prey.

name: kabuto
flavor_text_en: A POKéMON that was resurrected from a fossilfound in what was once the ocean floor eons ago.

name: kabutops
flavor_text_en: Its sleek shape is perfect for swim­ ming. It slashesprey with its claws and drains the body fluids.

name: aerodactyl
flavor_text_en: A Pokémon that roamed the skies in the dinosaur era. Its teeth are like saw blades.

name: snorlax
flavor_text_en: Very lazy. Just eats and sleeps. As its rotundbulk builds, it becomes steadily more slothful.

name: articuno
flavor_text_en: A legendary bird POKéMON that is said to appear todoomed people who are lost in icy mountains.

name: zapdos
flavor_text_en: A legendary bird POKéMON that is said to appearfrom clouds while dropping enormous lightning bolts.

name: moltres
flavor_text_en: Known as the legendary bird of fire. Every flapof its wings creates a dazzling flash of flames.

name: dratini
flavor_text_en: Long considered a mythical POKéMON until recentlywhen a small colony was found living underwater.

name: dragonair
flavor_text_en: A mystical POKéMON that exudes a gentle aura.Has the ability to change climate conditions.

name: dragonite
flavor_text_en: An extremely rarely seen marine POKéMON.Its intelligence is said to match that of humans.

name: mewtwo
flavor_text_en: It was created by a scientist after years of horrificgene splicing and DNA engineering experiments.

name: mew
flavor_text_en: So rare that it is still said to be a mirage bymany experts. Only a few people have seen it worldwide.

name: chikorita
flavor_text_en: A sweet aroma gently wafts from the leaf on itshead. It is docile and loves to soak up the sun's rays.

name: bayleef
flavor_text_en: The scent of spices comes from around its neck.Somehow, sniffing it makes you want to fight.

name: meganium
flavor_text_en: The aroma that rises from its petals contains asubstance that calms aggressive feelings.

name: cyndaquil
flavor_text_en: It has a timid nature. If it is startled, the flames on its back burn more vigorously.

name: quilava
flavor_text_en: Be careful if it turns its back during battle. Itmeans that it will attack with the fire on its back.

name: typhlosion
flavor_text_en: If its rage peaks, it becomes so hot that anything thattouches it will instantly go up in flames.

name: totodile
flavor_text_en: Its well-developed jaws are powerful and capable ofcrushing anything. Even its trainer must be careful.

name: croconaw
flavor_text_en: If it loses a fang, a new one grows back in itsplace. There are always 48 fangs lining its mouth.

name: feraligatr
flavor_text_en: When it bites with its massive and powerful jaws, itshakes its head and savagely tears its victim up.

name: sentret
flavor_text_en: A very cautious POKéMON, it raises itself up usingits tail to get a better view of its surroundings.

name: furret
flavor_text_en: It makes a nest to suit its long and skinny body. Thenest is impossible for other POKéMON to enter.

name: hoothoot
flavor_text_en: It always stands on one foot. It changes feet sofast, the movement can rarely be seen.

name: noctowl
flavor_text_en: Its eyes are specially adapted. They concentrateeven faint light and enable it to see in the dark.

name: ledyba
flavor_text_en: It is very timid. It will be afraid to move if it isalone. But it will be active if it is in a group.

name: ledian
flavor_text_en: When the stars flicker in the night sky, itflutters about, scattering a glowing powder.

name: spinarak
flavor_text_en: It lies still in the same pose for days in its web,waiting for its unsuspecting prey to wander close.

name: ariados
flavor_text_en: It spins string not only from its rear but also fromits mouth. It is hard to tell which end is which.

name: crobat
flavor_text_en: It flies so si­ lently through the dark on its fourwings that it may not be noticed even when nearby.

name: chinchou
flavor_text_en: Chinchou blink their shining antennae at one another to claim their respective turf.

name: lanturn
flavor_text_en: The light it emits is so bright that it can illuminatethe sea's surface from a depth of over three miles.

name: pichu
flavor_text_en: It is not yet skilled at storing electricity.It may send out a jolt if amused or startled.

name: cleffa
flavor_text_en: Because of its unusual, star-like silhouette, peoplebelieve that it came here on a meteor.

name: igglybuff
flavor_text_en: It has a very soft body. If it starts to roll, it willbounce all over and be impossible to stop.

name: togepi
flavor_text_en: The shell seems to be filled with joy. It is saidthat it will share good luck when treated kindly.

name: togetic
flavor_text_en: They say that it will appear before kindhearted, car­ing people and shower them with happiness.

name: natu
flavor_text_en: Because its wings aren't yet fully grown, it has tohop to get around. It is always star­ ing at something.

name: xatu
flavor_text_en: They say that it stays still and quiet because itis seeing both the past and future at the same time.

name: mareep
flavor_text_en: If static elec­ tricity builds in its body, itsfleece doubles in volume. Touching it will shock you.

name: flaaffy
flavor_text_en: As a result of storing too much electricity, itdeveloped patches where even downy wool won't grow.

name: ampharos
flavor_text_en: The tail's tip shines brightly and can be seenfrom far away. It acts as a beacon for lost people.

name: bellossom
flavor_text_en: Plentiful in the tropics. When it dances, its petals rub together and make a pleasant ringing sound.

name: marill
flavor_text_en: The tip of its tail, which con­ tains oil that islighter than wa­ ter, lets it swim without drowning.

name: azumarill
flavor_text_en: It lives in water virtually all day long. Its body color and pattern act as camouflage that makes it tough for enemies to spot in water.

name: sudowoodo
flavor_text_en: Although it always pretends to be a tree, its composi­tion appears to be closer to a rock than a plant.

name: politoed
flavor_text_en: If POLIWAG and POLIWHIRL hear its echoing cry, theyrespond by gather­ ing from far and wide.

name: hoppip
flavor_text_en: To keep from being blown away by the wind, they gatherin clusters. They do enjoy gentle breezes, though.

name: skiploom
flavor_text_en: The bloom on top of its head opens and closes as thetemperature fluc­ tuates up and down.

name: jumpluff
flavor_text_en: Once it catches the wind, it deft­ ly controls itscotton-puff spores to float, even around the world.

name: aipom
flavor_text_en: Its tail is so powerful that it can use it to graba tree branch and hold itself up in the air.

name: sunkern
flavor_text_en: It may drop out of the sky suddenly. If attacked by aSPEAROW, it will violently shake its leaves.

name: sunflora
flavor_text_en: It converts sun­ light into energy. In the darknessafter sunset, it closes its petals and becomes still.

name: yanma
flavor_text_en: If it flaps its wings really fast, it can generateshock waves that will shatter win­ dows in the area.

name: wooper
flavor_text_en: This POKéMON lives in cold water. It will leave thewater to search for food when it gets cold outside.

name: quagsire
flavor_text_en: This carefree POKéMON has an easy-going nature.While swimming, it always bumps into boat hulls.

name: espeon
flavor_text_en: It uses the fine hair that covers its body to senseair currents and predict its ene­ my's actions.

name: umbreon
flavor_text_en: When agitated, this POKéMON pro­ tects itself byspraying poisonous sweat from its pores.

name: murkrow
flavor_text_en: Feared and loathed by many, it is believed to bringmisfortune to all those who see it at night.

name: slowking
flavor_text_en: It has incredible intellect and in­ tuition. Whateverthe situation, it remains calm and collected.

name: misdreavus
flavor_text_en: It likes playing mischievous tricks such as screamingand wailing to startle people at night.

name: unown
flavor_text_en: Their shapes look like hieroglyphs on ancient tab­lets. It is said that the two are somehow related.

name: wobbuffet
flavor_text_en: It hates light and shock. If attack­ ed, it inflatesits body to pump up its counter­ strike.

name: girafarig
flavor_text_en: Its tail has a small brain of its own. Beware! Ifyou get close, it may react to your scent and bite.

name: pineco
flavor_text_en: It likes to make its shell thicker by adding layersof tree bark. The additional weight doesn't bother it.

name: forretress
flavor_text_en: Its entire body is shielded by a steel-hard shell.What lurks inside the armor is a total mystery.

name: dunsparce
flavor_text_en: When spotted, this POKéMON escapes backward by furi­ously boring into the ground with its tail.

name: gligar
flavor_text_en: It flies straight at its target's face then clampsdown on the star­ tled victim to inject poison.

name: steelix
flavor_text_en: It is thought its body transformed as a result of iron accumulating internally from swallowing soil.

name: snubbull
flavor_text_en: Although it looks frightening, it is actually kind andaffectionate. It is very popular among women.

name: granbull
flavor_text_en: It is actually timid and easily spooked. If at­tacked, it flails about to fend off its attacker.

name: qwilfish
flavor_text_en: To fire its poison spikes, it must inflate its bodyby drinking over 2.6 gallons of water all at once.

name: scizor
flavor_text_en: It has a steel-hard body. It intimidates foes by upraising its eye-patterned pincers.

name: shuckle
flavor_text_en: The BERRIES it stores in its vase-like shelldecompose and become a gooey liquid.

name: heracross
flavor_text_en: It is usually docile, but if it is disturbed while sipping honey, it chases off the intruder with its horn.

name: sneasel
flavor_text_en: Its paws conceal sharp claws. If attacked, it sud­denly extends the claws and startles its enemy.

name: teddiursa
flavor_text_en: If it finds honey, its crescent mark glows. It alwayslicks its paws because they are soaked with honey.

name: ursaring
flavor_text_en: Although it is a good climber, it prefers to snaptrees with its forelegs and eat fallen BERRIES.

name: slugma
flavor_text_en: It never sleeps. It has to keep moving because ifit stopped, its magma body would cool and harden.

name: magcargo
flavor_text_en: The shell on its back is just skin that has cooledand hardened. It breaks easily with a slight touch.

name: swinub
flavor_text_en: It rubs its snout on the ground to find and dig upfood. It sometimes discovers hot springs.

name: piloswine
flavor_text_en: Because the long hair all over its body obscures itssight, it just keeps charging repeatedly.

name: corsola
flavor_text_en: It continuously sheds and grows. The tip of itshead is prized as a treasure for its beauty.

name: remoraid
flavor_text_en: It has superb ac­ curacy. The water it shoots out canstrike even moving prey from more than 300 feet.

name: octillery
flavor_text_en: It traps enemies with its suction- cupped tentaclesthen smashes them with its rock-hard head.

name: delibird
flavor_text_en: It carries food all day long. There are talesabout lost people who were saved by the food it had.

name: mantine
flavor_text_en: As it majestically swims, it doesn't care if REMORAIDattach to it for scavenging its leftovers.

name: skarmory
flavor_text_en: Its sturdy wings look heavy, but they are actuallyhollow and light, allowing it to fly freely in the sky.

name: houndour
flavor_text_en: It uses different kinds of cries for communicating withothers of its kind and for pursuing its prey.

name: houndoom
flavor_text_en: If you are burned by the flames it shoots from itsmouth, the pain will never go away.

name: kingdra
flavor_text_en: It is said that it usually hides in underwater caves.It can create whirlpools by yawning.

name: phanpy
flavor_text_en: It swings its long snout around play­ fully, but becauseit is so strong, that can be dan­ gerous.

name: donphan
flavor_text_en: It has sharp, hard tusks and a rugged hide. Its TACKLEis strong enough to knock down a house.

name: porygon2
flavor_text_en: This upgraded version of PORYGON is designed forspace exploration. It can't fly, though.

name: stantler
flavor_text_en: The curved antlers subtly change the flow of air tocreate a strange space where real­ ity is distorted.

name: smeargle
flavor_text_en: A special fluid oozes from the tip of its tail. Itpaints the fluid everywhere to mark its territory.

name: tyrogue
flavor_text_en: It is always bursting with en­ ergy. To make it­self stronger, it keeps on fighting even if it loses.

name: hitmontop
flavor_text_en: If you become enchanted by its smooth, elegant,dance-like kicks, you may get drilled hard.

name: smoochum
flavor_text_en: Its lips are the most sensitive parts on its body.It always uses its lips first to examine things.

name: elekid
flavor_text_en: It rotates its arms to generate electricity, butit tires easily, so it charges up only a little bit.

name: magby
flavor_text_en: Each and every time it inhales and exhales, hotembers dribble out of its mouth and nostrils.

name: miltank
flavor_text_en: Its milk is packed with nutrition, making it theultimate beverage for the sick or weary.

name: blissey
flavor_text_en: Anyone who takes even one bite of BLISSEY's egg be­comes unfailingly caring and pleas­ ant to everyone.

name: raikou
flavor_text_en: The rain clouds it carries let it fire thunderboltsat will. They say that it descended with lightning.

name: entei
flavor_text_en: Volcanoes erupt when it barks. Un­ able to restrainits extreme power, it races headlong around the land.

name: suicune
flavor_text_en: It races around the world to purify fouled water. It dashes away with the north wind.

name: larvitar
flavor_text_en: It feeds on soil. After it has eaten a large mountain,it will fall asleep so it can grow.

name: pupitar
flavor_text_en: Its shell is as hard as sheet rock, and it isalso very strong. Its THRASHING can topple a mountain.

name: tyranitar
flavor_text_en: Its body can't be harmed by any sort of attack, so itis very eager to make challenges against enemies.

name: lugia
flavor_text_en: It is said that it quietly spends its time deep at thebottom of the sea because its powers are too strong.

name: ho-oh
flavor_text_en: Legends claim this POKéMON flies the world's skies con­tinuously on its magnificent seven- colored wings.

name: celebi
flavor_text_en: This POKéMON wan­ ders across time. Grass and treesflourish in the forests in which it has appeared.

name: treecko
flavor_text_en: TREECKO has small hooks on the bottom of its feet that enable it to scale vertical walls.This POKéMON attacks by slamming foes with its thick tail.

name: grovyle
flavor_text_en: The leaves growing out of GROVYLE’s body are convenient for camouflaging it from enemies in the forest.This POKéMON is a master at climbing trees in jungles.

name: sceptile
flavor_text_en: The leaves growing on SCEPTILE’s body are very sharp edged. This POKéMON is very agile - it leaps all over thebranches of trees and jumps on its foe from above or behind.

name: torchic
flavor_text_en: TORCHIC sticks with its TRAINER, following behind with unsteady steps.This POKéMON breathes fire of over 1,800 degrees F, including fireballs that leave the foe scorched black.

name: combusken
flavor_text_en: COMBUSKEN toughens up its legs and thighs by running through fields and mountains.This POKéMON’s legs possess both speed and power, enabling it to dole out ten kicks in one second.

name: blaziken
flavor_text_en: In battle, BLAZIKEN blows out intense flames from its wrists and attacks foes courageously.The stronger the foe, the more intensely this POKéMON’s wrists burn.

name: mudkip
flavor_text_en: The fin on MUDKIP’s head acts as highly sensitive radar. Using this fin to sense movements of water and air, thisPOKéMON can determine what is taking place around it without using its eyes.

name: marshtomp
flavor_text_en: The surface of MARSHTOMP’s body is enveloped by a thin, sticky film that enables it to live on land.This POKéMON plays in mud on beaches when the ocean tide is low.

name: swampert
flavor_text_en: SWAMPERT is very strong. It has enough power to easily drag a boulder weighing more than a ton.This POKéMON also has powerful vision that lets it see even in murky water.

name: poochyena
flavor_text_en: At first sight, POOCHYENA takes a bite at anything that moves. This POKéMON chases after prey untilthe victim becomes exhausted. However, it may turn tail if the prey strikes back.

name: mightyena
flavor_text_en: MIGHTYENA gives obvious signals when it is preparing to attack. It starts to growl deeply and then flattens its body.This POKéMON will bite savagely with its sharply pointed fangs.

name: zigzagoon
flavor_text_en: ZIGZAGOON restlessly wanders everywhere at all times. This POKéMON does so because it is very curious.It becomes interested in anything that it happens to see.

name: linoone
flavor_text_en: LINOONE always runs full speed and only in straight lines. If facing an obstacle, it makes a right-angle turn to evade it.This POKéMON is very challenged by gently curving roads.

name: wurmple
flavor_text_en: Using the spikes on its rear end,   WURMPLE peels the bark off trees and feeds on the sap that oozes out.This POKéMON’s feet are tipped with suction pads that allow it to cling to glass without slipping.

name: silcoon
flavor_text_en: SILCOON tethers itself to a tree branch using silk to keep from falling. There,  this POKéMON hangs quietly while itawaits evolution. It peers out of the silk cocoon through a small hole.

name: beautifly
flavor_text_en: BEAUTIFLY’s favorite food is the sweet pollen of flowers. If you want to see this POKéMON, just leave a pottedflower by an open window. BEAUTIFLY is sure to come looking for pollen.

name: cascoon
flavor_text_en: CASCOON makes its protective cocoon by wrapping its body entirely with a fine silk from its mouth. Once the silkgoes around its body, it hardens. This POKéMON prepares for its evolution inside the cocoon.

name: dustox
flavor_text_en: DUSTOX is instinctively drawn to light. Swarms of this POKéMON are attracted by the bright lights of cities, wherethey wreak havoc by stripping the leaves off roadside trees for food.

name: lotad
flavor_text_en: It searches about for clean water. If it does not drink water for too long, the leaf on its head wilts.

name: lombre
flavor_text_en: It lives at the water’s edge where it is sunny. It sleeps on a bed of water grass by day and becomes active at night.

name: ludicolo
flavor_text_en: LUDICOLO begins dancing as soon as it hears cheerful, festive music. This POKéMON is said to appear when ithears the singing of children on hiking outings.

name: seedot
flavor_text_en: SEEDOT attaches itself to a tree branch using the top of its head. It sucks moisture from the tree whilehanging off the branch. The more water it drinks, the glossier this POKéMON’s body becomes.

name: nuzleaf
flavor_text_en: NUZLEAF live in densely overgrown forests. They occasionally venture out of the forest to startle people.This POKéMON dislikes having its long nose pinched.

name: shiftry
flavor_text_en: It lives quietly in the deep forest. It is said to create chilly winter winds with the fans it holds.

name: taillow
flavor_text_en: TAILLOW courageously stands its ground against foes, however strong they may be.This gutsy POKéMON will remain defiant even after a loss. On the other hand, it cries loudly if it becomes hungry.

name: swellow
flavor_text_en: SWELLOW flies high above our heads, making graceful arcs in the sky. This POKéMON dives at a steep angle assoon as it spots its prey. The hapless prey is tightly grasped by SWELLOW’s clawed feet, preventing escape.

name: wingull
flavor_text_en: WINGULL has the habit of carrying prey and valuables in its beak and hiding them in all sorts of locations.This POKéMON rides the winds and flies as if it were skating across the sky.

name: pelipper
flavor_text_en: It is a messenger of the skies, carrying small Pokémon and eggs to safety in its bill.

name: ralts
flavor_text_en: RALTS senses the emotions of people using the horns on its head. This POKéMON rarely appears beforepeople. But when it does, it draws closer if it senses that the person has a positive disposition.

name: kirlia
flavor_text_en: It is said that a KIRLIA that is exposed to the positive emotions of its TRAINER grows beautiful.This POKéMON controls psychokinetic powers with its highly developed brain.

name: gardevoir
flavor_text_en: GARDEVOIR has the ability to read the future. If it senses impending danger to its TRAINER, this POKéMON is said tounleash its psychokinetic energy at full power.

name: surskit
flavor_text_en: From the tips of its feet, SURSKIT secretes an oil that enables it to walk on water as if it were skating.This POKéMON feeds on microscopic organisms in ponds and lakes.

name: masquerain
flavor_text_en: MASQUERAIN intimidates enemies with the eyelike patterns on its antennas. This POKéMON flaps its four wings tofreely fly in any direction - even sideways and backwards - as if it were a helicopter.

name: shroomish
flavor_text_en: SHROOMISH live in damp soil in the dark depths of forests. They are often found keeping still under fallen leaves.This POKéMON feeds on compost that is made up of fallen, rotted leaves.

name: breloom
flavor_text_en: BRELOOM closes in on its foe with light and sprightly footwork, then throws punches with its stretchy arms.This POKéMON’s fighting technique puts boxers to shame.

name: slakoth
flavor_text_en: SLAKOTH lolls around for over twenty hours every day. Because it moves so little, it does not need much food.This POKéMON’s sole daily meal consists of just three leaves.

name: vigoroth
flavor_text_en: VIGOROTH is always itching and agitated to go on a wild rampage. It simply can’t tolerate sitting still for even a minute.This POKéMON’s stress level rises if it can’t be moving constantly.

name: slaking
flavor_text_en: SLAKING spends all day lying down and lolling about. It eats grass growing within its reach.If it eats all the grass it can reach, this POKéMON reluctantly moves to another spot.

name: nincada
flavor_text_en: NINCADA lives underground for many years in complete darkness. This POKéMON absorbs nutrients fromthe roots of trees. It stays motionless as it waits for evolution.

name: ninjask
flavor_text_en: NINJASK moves around at such a high speed that it cannot be seen, even while its crying can be clearly heard.For that reason, this POKéMON was long believed to be invisible.

name: shedinja
flavor_text_en: SHEDINJA’s hard body doesn’t move - not even a twitch. In fact, its body appears to be merely a hollow shell.It is believed that this POKéMON will steal the spirit of anyone peering into its hollow body from its back.

name: whismur
flavor_text_en: Normally, WHISMUR’s voice is very quiet - it is barely audible even if one is paying close attention.However, if this POKéMON senses danger, it starts crying at an earsplitting volume.

name: loudred
flavor_text_en: LOUDRED’s bellowing can completely decimate a wood-frame house. It uses its voice to punish its foes.This POKéMON’s round ears serve as loudspeakers.

name: exploud
flavor_text_en: EXPLOUD triggers earthquakes with the tremors it creates by bellowing. If this POKéMON violently inhales from theports on its body, it’s a sign that it is preparing to let loose a huge bellow.

name: makuhita
flavor_text_en: MAKUHITA is tenacious - it will keep getting up and attacking its foe however many times it is knocked down.Every time it gets back up, this POKéMON stores more energy in its body for evolving.

name: hariyama
flavor_text_en: It has the habit of challenging others without hesitation to tests of strength. It’s been known to stand on train tracks and stop trains using forearm thrusts.

name: azurill
flavor_text_en: A Pokémon that lives by water. It moves quickly on land by bouncing on its big tail.

name: nosepass
flavor_text_en: NOSEPASS’s magnetic nose is always pointed to the north. If two of these POKéMON meet, they cannot turntheir faces to each other when they are close because their magnetic noses repel one another.

name: skitty
flavor_text_en: SKITTY has the habit of becoming fascinated by moving objects and chasing them around.This POKéMON is known to chase after its own tail and become dizzy.

name: delcatty
flavor_text_en: DELCATTY prefers to live an unfettered existence in which it can do as it pleases at its own pace.Because this POKéMON eats and sleeps whenever it decides, its daily routines are completely random.

name: sableye
flavor_text_en: SABLEYE lead quiet lives deep inside caverns. They are feared, however, because these POKéMON are thought tosteal the spirits of people when their eyes burn with a sinister glow in the darkness.

name: mawile
flavor_text_en: MAWHILE’s huge jaws are actually steel horns that have been transformed. Its docile-looking face serves to lullits foe into letting down its guard. When the foe least expects it, MAWHILE chomps it with its gaping jaws.

name: aron
flavor_text_en: This POKéMON has a body of steel. To make its body, ARON feeds on iron ore that it digs from mountains.Occasionally, it causes major trouble by eating bridges and rails.

name: lairon
flavor_text_en: LAIRON tempers its steel body by drinking highly nutritious mineral springwater until it is bloated.This POKéMON makes its nest close to springs of delicious water.

name: aggron
flavor_text_en: AGGRON claims an entire mountain as its own territory. It mercilessly beats up anything that violates its environment.This POKéMON vigilantly patrols its territory at all times.

name: meditite
flavor_text_en: MEDITITE undertakes rigorous mental training deep in the mountains. However, whenever it meditates, thisPOKéMON always loses its concentration and focus. As a result, its training never ends.

name: medicham
flavor_text_en: It is said that through meditation, MEDICHAM heightens energy inside its body and sharpens its sixth sense.This POKéMON hides its presence by merging itself with fields and mountains.

name: electrike
flavor_text_en: ELECTRIKE stores electricity in its long body hair. This POKéMON stimulates its leg muscles with electric charges.These jolts of power give its legs explosive acceleration performance.

name: manectric
flavor_text_en: MANECTRIC is constantly discharging electricity from its mane. The sparks sometimes ignite forest fires.When it enters a battle, this POKéMON creates thunderclouds.

name: plusle
flavor_text_en: PLUSLE always acts as a cheerleader for its partners. Whenever a teammate puts out a good effort in battle, thisPOKéMON shorts out its body to create the crackling noises of sparks to show its joy.

name: minun
flavor_text_en: MINUN is more concerned about cheering on its partners than its own safety. It shorts out the electricity in itsbody to create brilliant showers of sparks to cheer on its teammates.

name: volbeat
flavor_text_en: With the arrival of night, VOLBEAT emits light from its tail. It communicates with others by adjusting the intensity andflashing of its light. This POKéMON is attracted by the sweet aroma of ILLUMISE.

name: illumise
flavor_text_en: With its sweet aroma, it guides Volbeat to draw signs with light in the night sky.

name: roselia
flavor_text_en: ROSELIA shoots sharp thorns as projectiles at any opponent that tries to steal the flowers on its arms.The aroma of this POKéMON brings serenity to living things.

name: gulpin
flavor_text_en: Virtually all of GULPIN’s body is its stomach. As a result, it can swallow something its own size.This POKéMON’s stomach contains a special fluid that digests anything.

name: swalot
flavor_text_en: When SWALOT spots prey, it spurts out a hideously toxic fluid from its pores and sprays the target.Once the prey has weakened, this POKéMON gulps it down whole with its cavernous mouth.

name: carvanha
flavor_text_en: CARVANHA’s strongly developed jaws and its sharply pointed fangs pack the destructive power to rip out boat hulls.Many boats have been attacked and sunk by this POKéMON.

name: sharpedo
flavor_text_en: Nicknamed “the bully of the sea,” SHARPEDO is widely feared. Its cruel fangs grow back immediatelyif they snap off. Just one of these POKéMON can thoroughly tear apart a supertanker.

name: wailmer
flavor_text_en: WAILMER’s nostrils are located above its eyes. This playful POKéMON loves to startle people by forcefully snortingout seawater it stores inside its body out of its nostrils.

name: wailord
flavor_text_en: WAILORD is the largest of all identified POKéMON up to now. This giant POKéMON swims languorouslyin the vast open sea, eating massive amounts of food at once with its enormous mouth.

name: numel
flavor_text_en: NUMEL is extremely dull witted - it doesn’t notice being hit. However, it can’t stand hunger for even a second.This POKéMON’s body is a seething cauldron of boiling magma.

name: camerupt
flavor_text_en: CAMERUPT has a volcano inside its body. Magma of 18,000 degrees F courses through its body.Occasionally, the humps on this POKéMON’s back erupt, spewing the superheated magma.

name: torkoal
flavor_text_en: You can tell how it’s feeling by the smoke spouting from its shell. Tremendous velocity is a sign of good health.

name: spoink
flavor_text_en: SPOINK bounces around on its tail. The shock of its bouncing makes its heart pump. As a result, this POKéMONcannot afford to stop bouncing - if it stops, its heart will stop.

name: grumpig
flavor_text_en: GRUMPIG uses the black pearls on its body to amplify its psychic power waves for gaining total control over its foe.When this POKéMON uses its special power, its snorting breath grows labored.

name: spinda
flavor_text_en: No two Spinda have the same pattern of spots. Its tottering step fouls the aim of foes.

name: trapinch
flavor_text_en: TRAPINCH’s nest is a sloped, bowl-like pit dug in sand. This POKéMON patiently waits for prey to tumble down the pit.Its giant jaws have enough strength to crush even boulders.

name: vibrava
flavor_text_en: To make prey faint, VIBRAVA generates ultrasonic waves by vigorously making its two wings vibrate.This POKéMON’s ultrasonic waves are so powerful, they can bring on headaches in people.

name: flygon
flavor_text_en: FLYGON is nicknamed “the elemental  spirit of the desert.” Because its flapping wings whip up a cloud of sand,this POKéMON is always enveloped in a sandstorm while flying.

name: cacnea
flavor_text_en: CACNEA lives in arid locations such as deserts. It releases a strong aroma from its flower to attract prey.When prey comes near, this POKéMON shoots sharp thorns from its body to bring the victim down.

name: cacturne
flavor_text_en: During the daytime, CACTURNE remains unmoving so that it does not lose any moisture to the harsh desert sun.This POKéMON becomes active at night when the temperature drops.

name: swablu
flavor_text_en: SWABLU has light and fluffy wings that are like cottony clouds. This POKéMON is not frightened of people.It lands on the heads of people and sits there like a cotton-fluff hat.

name: altaria
flavor_text_en: ALTARIA dances and wheels through the sky among billowing, cotton-like clouds. By singing melodies in its crystal-clearvoice, this POKéMON makes its listeners experience dreamy wonderment.

name: zangoose
flavor_text_en: Memories of battling its arch-rival SEVIPER are etched into every cell of ZANGOOSE’s body.This POKéMON adroitly dodges attacks with incredible agility.

name: seviper
flavor_text_en: SEVIPER shares a generations-long feud with ZANGOOSE. The scars on its body are evidence of vicious battles.This POKéMON attacks using its sword- edged tail.

name: lunatone
flavor_text_en: LUNATONE was discovered at a location where a meteorite fell. As a result, some people theorize that this POKéMONcame from space. However, no one has been able to prove this theory so far.

name: solrock
flavor_text_en: Solar energy is the source of its power, so it is strong during the daytime. When it spins, its body shines.

name: barboach
flavor_text_en: BARBOACH’s sensitive whiskers serve as a superb radar system. This POKéMON hides in mud, leaving onlyits two whiskers exposed while it waits for prey to come along.

name: whiscash
flavor_text_en: WHISCASH is extremely territorial. Just one of these POKéMON will claim a large pond as its exclusive territory.If a foe approaches it, it thrashes about and triggers a massive earthquake.

name: corphish
flavor_text_en: Its hardy vitality enables it to adapt to any environment. Its pincers will never release prey.

name: crawdaunt
flavor_text_en: CRAWDAUNT has an extremely violent nature that compels it to challenge other living things to battle.Other life-forms refuse to live in ponds inhabited by this POKéMON, making them desolate places.

name: baltoy
flavor_text_en: BALTOY moves while spinning around on its one foot. Primitive wall paintings depicting this POKéMON living amongpeople were discovered in some ancient ruins.

name: claydol
flavor_text_en: CLAYDOL are said to be dolls of mud made by primitive humans and brought to life by exposure to a mysterious ray.This POKéMON moves about while levitating.

name: lileep
flavor_text_en: LILEEP became extinct approximately a hundred million years ago. This ancient POKéMON attaches itselfto a rock on the seafloor and catches approaching prey using tentacles  shaped like flower petals.

name: cradily
flavor_text_en: CRADILY roams around the ocean floor in search of food. This POKéMON freely extends its tree trunk-like neck andcaptures unwary prey using its eight tentacles.

name: anorith
flavor_text_en: ANORITH was regenerated from a prehistoric fossil. This primitive POKéMON once lived in warm seas.It grips its prey firmly between its two large claws.

name: armaldo
flavor_text_en: ARMALDO’s tough armor makes all attacks bounce off. This POKéMON’s two enormous claws can be freely extendedor contracted. They have the power to punch right through a steel slab.

name: feebas
flavor_text_en: FEEBAS’s fins are ragged and tattered from the start of its life. Because of its shoddy appearance, thisPOKéMON is largely ignored. It is capable of living in both the sea and in rivers.

name: milotic
flavor_text_en: Its lovely scales are described as rainbow colored. They change color depending on the viewing angle.

name: castform
flavor_text_en: CASTFORM’s appearance changes with the weather. This POKéMON gained the ability to usethe vast power of nature to protect its tiny body.

name: kecleon
flavor_text_en: It changes body color to blend in with its surroundings. It also changes color if it is happy or sad.

name: shuppet
flavor_text_en: SHUPPET is attracted by feelings of jealousy and vindictiveness. If someone develops strong feelings ofvengeance, this POKéMON will appear in a swarm and line up beneath the eaves of that person’s home.

name: banette
flavor_text_en: BANETTE generates energy for laying strong curses by sticking pins into its own body.This POKéMON was originally a pitiful plush doll that was thrown away.

name: duskull
flavor_text_en: DUSKULL can pass through any wall no matter how thick it may be. Once this POKéMON chooses a target,it will doggedly pursue the intended victim until the break of dawn.

name: dusclops
flavor_text_en: DUSCLOPS’s body is completely hollow - there is nothing at all inside. It is said that its body is like a blackhole. This POKéMON will absorb anything into its body, but nothing will ever come back out.

name: tropius
flavor_text_en: The bunches of fruit around TROPIUS’s neck are very popular with children. This POKéMON loves fruit, and eats itcontinuously. Apparently, its love for fruit resulted in its own outgrowth of fruit.

name: chimecho
flavor_text_en: CHIMECHO makes its cries echo inside its hollow body. When this POKéMON becomes enraged, its criesresult in ultrasonic waves that have the power to knock foes flying.

name: absol
flavor_text_en: Every time ABSOL appears before people, it is followed by a disaster such as an earthquake or a tidal wave.As a result, it came to be known as the disaster POKéMON.

name: wynaut
flavor_text_en: WYNAUT can always be seen with a big, happy smile on its face. Look at its tail to determine if it is angry.When angered, this POKéMON will be slapping the ground with its tail.

name: snorunt
flavor_text_en: SNORUNT live in regions with heavy snowfall. In seasons without snow, such as spring and summer, this POKéMONsteals away to live quietly among stalactites and stalagmites deep in caverns.

name: glalie
flavor_text_en: GLALIE has a body made of rock, which it hardens with an armor of ice. This POKéMON has the ability to freezemoisture in the atmosphere into any shape it desires.

name: spheal
flavor_text_en: SPHEAL is much faster rolling than  walking to get around. When groups of this POKéMON eat, they all clap at onceto show their pleasure. Because of this, their mealtimes are noisy.

name: sealeo
flavor_text_en: SEALEO has the habit of always juggling on the tip of its nose anything it sees for the first time.This POKéMON occasionally entertains itself by balancing and rolling a SPHEAL on its nose.

name: walrein
flavor_text_en: It swims through icy seas while shattering ice floes with its large tusks. It is protected by its thick blubber.

name: clamperl
flavor_text_en: CLAMPERL’s sturdy shell is not only good for protection - it is also used for clamping and catching prey.A fully grown CLAMPERL’s shell will be scored with nicks and scratches all over.

name: huntail
flavor_text_en: HUNTAIL’s presence went unnoticed by people for a long time because it lives at extreme depths in the sea.This POKéMON’s eyes can see clearly even in the murky dark depths of the ocean.

name: gorebyss
flavor_text_en: GOREBYSS lives in the southern seas at extreme depths. Its body is built to withstand the enormous pressure ofwater at incredible depths. Because of this, this POKéMON’s body is unharmed by ordinary attacks.

name: relicanth
flavor_text_en: RELICANTH is a POKéMON species that existed for a hundred million years without ever changing its form.This ancient POKéMON feeds on microscopic organisms with its toothless mouth.

name: luvdisc
flavor_text_en: LUVDISC live in shallow seas in the tropics. This heart-shaped POKéMON earned its name by swimming afterloving couples it spotted in the ocean’s waves.

name: bagon
flavor_text_en: Dreaming of one day flying, it practices by leaping off cliffs every day.

name: shelgon
flavor_text_en: Inside SHELGON’s armor-like shell, cells are in the midst of transformation to create an entirely new body.This POKéMON’s shell is extremely heavy, making its movements sluggish.

name: salamence
flavor_text_en: SALAMENCE came about as a result of a strong, long-held dream of growing wings. It is said that this powerfuldesire triggered a sudden mutation in this POKéMON’s cells, causing it to sprout its magnificent wings.

name: beldum
flavor_text_en: Instead of blood, a powerful magnetic force courses throughout BELDUM’s body. This POKéMON communicates withothers by sending controlled pulses of magnetism.

name: metang
flavor_text_en: When two BELDUM fuse together, METANG is formed. The brains of the BELDUM are joined by a magnetic nervous system.By linking its brains magnetically, this POKéMON generates strong psychokinetic power.

name: metagross
flavor_text_en: METAGROSS has four brains in total. Combined, the four brains can breeze through difficult calculations fasterthan a supercomputer. This POKéMON can float in the air by tucking in its four legs.

name: regirock
flavor_text_en: Its entire body is made of rock. If any part chips off in battle, it attaches rocks to repair itself.

name: regice
flavor_text_en: REGICE’s body was made during an ice age. The deep-frozen body can’t be melted, even by fire.This POKéMON controls frigid air of minus 328 degrees F.

name: registeel
flavor_text_en: REGISTEEL has a body that is harder than any kind of metal. Its body is apparently hollow.No one has any idea what this POKéMON eats.

name: latias
flavor_text_en: LATIAS is highly sensitive to the emotions of people. If it senses any hostility, this POKéMON ruffles thefeathers all over its body and cries shrilly to intimidate the foe.

name: latios
flavor_text_en: LATIOS has the ability to make its foe see an image of what it has seen or imagines in its head.This POKéMON is intelligent and understands human speech.

name: kyogre
flavor_text_en: KYOGRE has the power to create massive rain clouds that cover the entire sky and bring about torrential downpours.This POKéMON saved people who were suffering from droughts.

name: groudon
flavor_text_en: GROUDON has long been described in  mythology as the POKéMON that raised lands and expanded continents.This POKéMON took to sleep after a cataclysmic battle with KYOGRE.

name: rayquaza
flavor_text_en: RAYQUAZA lived for hundreds of millions of years in the earth’s ozone layer,  never descending to the ground.This POKéMON appears to feed on water and particles in the atmosphere.

name: jirachi
flavor_text_en: A legend states that JIRACHI will make true any wish that is written on notes attached to its head when it awakens.If this POKéMON senses danger, it will fight without awakening.

name: deoxys
flavor_text_en: The DNA of a space virus underwent a sudden mutation upon exposure to a laser beam and resulted in DEOXYS.The crystalline organ on this POKéMON’s chest appears to be its brain.

name: turtwig
flavor_text_en: Made from soil, the shell on its back hardens when it drinks water. It lives along lakes.

name: grotle
flavor_text_en: It knows where pure water wells up. It carries fellow Pokémon there on its back.

name: torterra
flavor_text_en: Small Pokémon occasionally gather on its unmoving back to begin building their nests.

name: chimchar
flavor_text_en: It agilely scales sheer cliffs to live atop craggy mountains. Its fire is put out when it sleeps.

name: monferno
flavor_text_en: To intimidate attackers, it stretches the fire on its tail to make itself appear bigger.

name: infernape
flavor_text_en: It uses a special kind of martial arts involving all its limbs. Its fire never goes out.

name: piplup
flavor_text_en: Because it is very proud, it hates accepting food from people. Its thick down guards it from cold.

name: prinplup
flavor_text_en: It lives alone, away from others. Apparently, every one of them believes it is the most important.

name: empoleon
flavor_text_en: The three horns that extend from its beak attest to its power. The leader has the biggest horns.

name: starly
flavor_text_en: They flock in great numbers. Though small, they flap their wings with great power.

name: staravia
flavor_text_en: It flies around forests and fields in search of bug Pokémon. It stays within a huge flock.

name: staraptor
flavor_text_en: It has a savage nature. It will courageously challenge foes that are much larger.

name: bidoof
flavor_text_en: With nerves of steel, nothing can perturb it. It is more agile and active than it appears.

name: bibarel
flavor_text_en: It makes its nest by damming streams with bark and mud. It is known as an industrious worker.

name: kricketot
flavor_text_en: It shakes its head back to front, causing its antennae to hit each other and sound like a xylophone.

name: kricketune
flavor_text_en: It crosses its knifelike arms in front of its chest when it cries. It can compose melodies ad lib.

name: shinx
flavor_text_en: All of its fur dazzles if danger is sensed. It flees while the foe is momentarily blinded.

name: luxio
flavor_text_en: Its claws loose electricity with enough amperage to cause fainting. They live in small groups.

name: luxray
flavor_text_en: It has eyes that can see through anything. It spots and captures prey hiding behind objects.

name: budew
flavor_text_en: Over the winter, it closes its bud and endures the cold. In spring, the bud opens and releases pollen.

name: roserade
flavor_text_en: It attracts prey with a sweet aroma, then downs it with thorny whips hidden in its arms.

name: cranidos
flavor_text_en: It lived in jungles around 100 million years ago. Its skull is as hard as iron.

name: rampardos
flavor_text_en: Its powerful head butt has enough power to shatter even the most durable things upon impact.

name: shieldon
flavor_text_en: A Pokémon that lived in jungles around 100 million years ago. Its facial hide is extremely hard.

name: bastiodon
flavor_text_en: Any frontal attack is repulsed. It is a docile Pokémon that feeds on grass and berries.

name: burmy
flavor_text_en: To shelter itself from cold, wintry winds, it covers itself with a cloak made of twigs and leaves.

name: wormadam
flavor_text_en: When BURMY evolved, its cloak became a part of this Pokémon’s body. The cloak is never shed.

name: mothim
flavor_text_en: It loves the honey of flowers and steals honey collected by COMBEE.

name: combee
flavor_text_en: A Pokémon formed by three others. It busily carries sweet floral honey to VESPIQUEN.

name: vespiquen
flavor_text_en: Its abdomen is a honeycomb for grubs. It raises its grubs on honey collected by COMBEE.

name: pachirisu
flavor_text_en: It makes fur balls that crackle with static electricity. It stores them with berries in tree holes.

name: buizel
flavor_text_en: It has a flotation sac that is like an inflatable collar. It floats on water with its head out.

name: floatzel
flavor_text_en: It floats using its well-developed flotation sac. It assists in the rescues of drowning people.

name: cherubi
flavor_text_en: The small ball holds the nutrients needed for evolution. Apparently, it is very sweet and tasty.

name: cherrim
flavor_text_en: It blooms during times of strong sunlight. It tries to make up for everything it endured as a bud.

name: shellos
flavor_text_en: Its colors and shapes differ from region to region. In the Sinnoh region, two types are confirmed.

name: gastrodon
flavor_text_en: It has a pliable body without any bones. If any part of its body is torn off, it grows right back.

name: ambipom
flavor_text_en: To eat, it deftly shucks nuts with its two tails. It rarely uses its arms now.

name: drifloon
flavor_text_en: A Pokémon formed by the spirits of people and Pokémon. It loves damp, humid seasons.

name: drifblim
flavor_text_en: At dusk, swarms of them are carried aloft on winds. When noticed, they suddenly vanish.

name: buneary
flavor_text_en: It slams foes by sharply uncoiling its rolled ears. It stings enough to make a grown-up cry in pain.

name: lopunny
flavor_text_en: An extremely cautious Pokémon. It cloaks its body with its fluffy ear fur when it senses danger.

name: mismagius
flavor_text_en: Its cries sound like incantations. Those hearing it are tormented by headaches and hallucinations.

name: honchkrow
flavor_text_en: Becoming active at night, it is known to swarm with numerous MURKROW in tow.

name: glameow
flavor_text_en: It claws if displeased and purrs when affectionate. Its fickleness is very popular among some.

name: purugly
flavor_text_en: It is a brazen brute that barges its way into another Pokémon’s nest and claims it as its own.

name: chingling
flavor_text_en: It emits cries by agitating an orb at the back of its throat. It moves with flouncing hops.

name: stunky
flavor_text_en: It protects itself by spraying a noxious fluid from its rear. The stench lingers for 24 hours.

name: skuntank
flavor_text_en: It sprays a vile-smelling fluid from the tip of its tail to attack. Its range is over 160 feet.

name: bronzor
flavor_text_en: Implements shaped like it were discovered in ancient tombs. It is unknown if they are related.

name: bronzong
flavor_text_en: One caused a news sensation when it was dug up at a construction site after a 2,000-year sleep.

name: bonsly
flavor_text_en: It looks as if it is always crying. It is actually adjusting its body’s fluid levels by eliminating excess.

name: mime-jr
flavor_text_en: It habitually mimics foes. Once mimicked, the foe cannot take its eyes off this Pokémon.

name: happiny
flavor_text_en: It loves round white things. It carries an egg-shaped rock in imitation of CHANSEY.

name: chatot
flavor_text_en: It can learn and speak human words. If they gather, they all learn the same saying.

name: spiritomb
flavor_text_en: A Pokémon that was formed by 108 spirits. It is bound to a fissure in an odd keystone.

name: gible
flavor_text_en: It nests in small, horizontal holes in cave walls. It pounces to catch prey that stray too close.

name: gabite
flavor_text_en: There is a long-held belief that medicine made from its scales will heal even incurable illnesses.

name: garchomp
flavor_text_en: When it folds up its body and extends its wings, it looks like a jet plane. It flies at sonic speed.

name: munchlax
flavor_text_en: It wolfs down its weight in food once a day, swallowing food whole with almost no chewing.

name: riolu
flavor_text_en: The aura that emanates from its body intensifies to alert others if it is afraid or sad.

name: lucario
flavor_text_en: It has the ability to sense the auras of all things. It understands human speech.

name: hippopotas
flavor_text_en: It lives in arid places. Instead of perspiration, it expels grainy sand from its body.

name: hippowdon
flavor_text_en: It blasts internally stored sand from ports on its body to create a towering twister for attack.

name: skorupi
flavor_text_en: It grips prey with its tail claws and injects poison. It tenaciously hangs on until the poison takes.

name: drapion
flavor_text_en: It has the power in its clawed arms to make scrap of a car. The tips of its claws release poison.

name: croagunk
flavor_text_en: Its cheeks hold poison sacs. It tries to catch foes off guard to jab them with toxic fingers.

name: toxicroak
flavor_text_en: Its knuckle claws secrete a toxin so vile that even a scratch could prove fatal.

name: carnivine
flavor_text_en: It attracts prey with its sweet- smelling saliva, then chomps down. It takes a whole day to eat prey.

name: finneon
flavor_text_en: After long exposure to sunlight, the patterns on its tail fins shine vividly when darkness arrives.

name: lumineon
flavor_text_en: It lives on the deep-sea floor. It attracts prey by flashing the patterns on its four tail fins.

name: mantyke
flavor_text_en: A friendly Pokémon that captures the subtle flows of seawater using its two antennae.

name: snover
flavor_text_en: It lives on snowy mountains. Having had little contact with humans, it is boldly inquisitive.

name: abomasnow
flavor_text_en: It whips up blizzards in mountains that are always buried in snow. It is the abominable snowman.

name: weavile
flavor_text_en: They live in cold regions, forming groups of four or five that hunt prey with impressive coordination.

name: magnezone
flavor_text_en: It evolved from exposure to a special magnetic field. Three units generate magnetism.

name: lickilicky
flavor_text_en: It wraps things with its extensible tongue. Getting too close to it will leave you soaked with drool.

name: rhyperior
flavor_text_en: It puts rocks in holes in its palms and uses its muscles to shoot them. GEODUDE are shot at rare times.

name: tangrowth
flavor_text_en: It ensnares prey by extending arms made of vines. Losing arms to predators does not trouble it.

name: electivire
flavor_text_en: As its electric charge amplifies, blue sparks begin to crackle between its horns.

name: magmortar
flavor_text_en: It blasts fireballs of over 3,600 degrees F from the ends of its arms. It lives in volcanic craters.

name: togekiss
flavor_text_en: It will never appear where there is strife. Its sightings have become rare recently.

name: yanmega
flavor_text_en: By churning its wings, it creates shock waves that inflict critical internal injuries to foes.

name: leafeon
flavor_text_en: Just like a plant, it uses photosynthesis. As a result, it is always enveloped in clear air.

name: glaceon
flavor_text_en: As a protective technique, it can completely freeze its fur to make its hairs stand like needles.

name: gliscor
flavor_text_en: It observes prey while hanging inverted from branches. When the chance presents itself, it swoops!

name: mamoswine
flavor_text_en: Its impressive tusks are made of ice. The population thinned when it turned warm after the ice age.

name: porygon-z
flavor_text_en: Additional software was installed to make it a better Pokémon. It began acting oddly, however.

name: gallade
flavor_text_en: A master of courtesy and swordsmanship, it fights using extending swords on its elbows.

name: probopass
flavor_text_en: It freely controls three small units called Mini-Noses using magnetic force.

name: dusknoir
flavor_text_en: The antenna on its head captures radio waves from the world of spirits that command it to take people there.

name: froslass
flavor_text_en: It freezes foes with an icy breath nearly -60 degrees F. What seems to be its body is actually hollow.

name: rotom
flavor_text_en: Its body is composed of plasma. It is known to infiltrate electronic devices and wreak havoc.

name: uxie
flavor_text_en: Known as “The Being of Knowledge.” It is said that it can wipe out the memory of those who see its eyes.

name: mesprit
flavor_text_en: Known as “The Being of Emotion.” It taught humans the nobility of sorrow, pain, and joy.

name: azelf
flavor_text_en: Known as “The Being of Willpower.” It sleeps at the bottom of a lake to keep the world in balance.

name: dialga
flavor_text_en: It has the power to control time. It appears in Sinnoh-region myths as an ancient deity.

name: palkia
flavor_text_en: It has the ability to distort space. It is described as a deity in Sinnoh-region mythology.

name: heatran
flavor_text_en: It dwells in volcanic caves. It digs in with its cross-shaped feet to crawl on ceilings and walls.

name: regigigas
flavor_text_en: There is an enduring legend that states this Pokémon towed continents with ropes.

name: giratina
flavor_text_en: A Pokémon that is said to live in a world on the reverse side of ours. It appears in an ancient cemetery.

name: cresselia
flavor_text_en: Shiny particles are released from its wings like a veil. It is said to represent the crescent moon.

name: phione
flavor_text_en: It drifts in warm seas. It always returns to where it was born, no matter how far it may have drifted.

name: manaphy
flavor_text_en: Born on a cold seafloor, it will swim great distances to return to its birthplace.

name: darkrai
flavor_text_en: It can lull people to sleep and make them dream. It is active during nights of the new moon.

name: shaymin
flavor_text_en: It lives in flower patches and avoids detection by curling up to look like a flowering plant.

name: arceus
flavor_text_en: It is described in mythology as the Pokémon that shaped the universe with its 1,000 arms.

name: sprigatito
flavor_text_en: Its fluffy fur is similar in composition to plants. This Pokémon frequently washes its face to keep it from drying out.

name: floragato
flavor_text_en: Floragato deftly wields the vine hidden beneath its long fur, slamming the hard flower bud against its opponents.

name: meowscarada
flavor_text_en: This Pokémon uses the reflective fur lining its cape to camouflage the stem of its flower, creating the illusion that the flower is floating.

name: fuecoco
flavor_text_en: It lies on warm rocks and uses the heat absorbed by its square-shaped scales to create fire energy.

name: crocalor
flavor_text_en: The combination of Crocalor’s fire energy and overflowing vitality has caused an egg-shaped fireball to appear on the Pokémon’s head.

name: skeledirge
flavor_text_en: The fiery bird changes shape when Skeledirge sings. Rumor has it that the bird was born when the fireball on Skeledirge’s head gained a soul.

name: quaxly
flavor_text_en: This Pokémon migrated to Paldea from distant lands long ago. The gel secreted by its feathers repels water and grime."

name: quaxwell
flavor_text_en: These Pokémon constantly run through shallow waters to train their legs, then compete with each other to see which of them kicks most gracefully.

name: quaquaval
flavor_text_en: A single kick from a Quaquaval can send a truck rolling. This Pokémon uses its powerful legs to perform striking dances from far-off lands.

name: lechonk
flavor_text_en: It searches for food all day. It possesses a keen sense of smell but doesn’t use it for anything other than foraging.

name: oinkologne
flavor_text_en: Oinkologne is proud of its fine, glossy skin. It emits a concentrated scent from the tip of its tail.

name: tarountula
flavor_text_en: The ball of threads wrapped around its body is elastic enough to deflect the scythes of Scyther, this Pokémon’s natural enemy.

name: spidops
flavor_text_en: It clings to branches and ceilings using its threads and moves without a sound. It takes out its prey before the prey even notices it.

name: nymble
flavor_text_en: It has its third set of legs folded up. When it’s in a tough spot, this Pokémon jumps over 30 feet using the strength of its legs.

name: lokix
flavor_text_en: When it decides to fight all out, it stands on its previously folded legs to enter Showdown Mode. It neutralizes its enemies in short order.

name: pawmi
flavor_text_en: It has underdeveloped electric sacs on its cheeks. These sacs can produce electricity only if Pawmi rubs them furiously with the pads on its forepaws.

name: pawmo
flavor_text_en: When its group is attacked, Pawmo is the first to leap into battle, defeating enemies with a fighting technique that utilizes electric shocks.

name: pawmot
flavor_text_en: This Pokémon normally is slow to react, but once it enters battle, it will strike down its enemies with lightning-fast movements.

name: tandemaus
flavor_text_en: Exhibiting great teamwork, they use their incisors to cut pieces out of any material that might be useful for a nest, then make off with them.

name: maushold
flavor_text_en: The two little ones just appeared one day. The group might be a family of related Pokémon, but nobody knows for sure.

name: fidough
flavor_text_en: This Pokémon is smooth and moist to the touch. Yeast in Fidough’s breath induces fermentation in the Pokémon’s vicinity.

name: dachsbun
flavor_text_en: The pleasant aroma that emanates from this Pokémon’s body helps wheat grow, so Dachsbun has been treasured by farming villages.

name: smoliv
flavor_text_en: It protects itself from enemies by emitting oil from the fruit on its head. This oil is bitter and astringent enough to make someone flinch.

name: dolliv
flavor_text_en: Dolliv shares its tasty, fresh-scented oil with others. This species has coexisted with humans since times long gone.

name: arboliva
flavor_text_en: This calm Pokémon is very compassionate. It will share its delicious, nutrient-rich oil with weakened Pokémon.

name: squawkabilly
flavor_text_en: These Pokémon prefer to live in cities. They form flocks based on the color of their feathers, and they fight over territory.

name: nacli
flavor_text_en: It was born in a layer of rock salt deep under the earth. This species was particularly treasured in the old days, as they would share precious salt.

name: naclstack
flavor_text_en: This Pokémon dry cures its prey by spraying salt over them. The curing process steals away the water in the prey’s body.

name: garganacl
flavor_text_en: Garganacl will rub its fingertips together and sprinkle injured Pokémon with salt. Even severe wounds will promptly heal afterward.

name: charcadet
flavor_text_en: Burnt charcoal came to life and became a Pokémon. Possessing a fiery fighting spirit, Charcadet will battle even tough opponents.

name: armarouge
flavor_text_en: Armarouge evolved through the use of a set of armor that belonged to a distinguished warrior. This Pokémon is incredibly loyal.

name: ceruledge
flavor_text_en: The fiery blades on its arms burn fiercely with the lingering resentment of a sword wielder who fell before accomplishing their goal.

name: tadbulb
flavor_text_en: Tadbulb shakes its tail to generate electricity. If it senses danger, it will make its head blink on and off to alert its allies.

name: bellibolt
flavor_text_en: When this Pokémon expands and contracts its wobbly body, the belly-button dynamo in its stomach produces a huge amount of electricity.

name: wattrel
flavor_text_en: When its wings catch the wind, the bones within produce electricity. This Pokémon dives into the ocean, catching prey by electrocuting them.

name: kilowattrel
flavor_text_en: Kilowattrel inflates its throat sac to amplify its electricity. By riding the wind, this Pokémon can fly over 430 miles in a day.

name: maschiff
flavor_text_en: It always scowls in an attempt to make opponents take it seriously, but even crying children will burst into laughter when they see Maschiff’s face.

name: mabosstiff
flavor_text_en: This Pokémon can store energy in its large dewlap. Mabosstiff unleashes this energy all at once to blow away enemies.

name: shroodle
flavor_text_en: Though usually a mellow Pokémon, it will sink its sharp, poison-soaked front teeth into any that anger it, causing paralysis in the object of its ire.

name: grafaiai
flavor_text_en: The color of the poisonous saliva depends on what the Pokémon eats. Grafaiai covers its fingers in its saliva and draws patterns on trees in forests.

name: bramblin
flavor_text_en: A soul unable to move on to the afterlife was blown around by the wind until it got tangled up with dried grass and became a Pokémon.

name: brambleghast
flavor_text_en: It will open the branches of its head to envelop its prey. Once it absorbs all the life energy it needs, it expels the prey and discards it.

name: toedscool
flavor_text_en: Toedscool lives in muggy forests. The flaps that fall from its body are chewy and very delicious.

name: toedscruel
flavor_text_en: These Pokémon gather into groups and form colonies deep within forests. They absolutely hate it when strangers approach.

name: klawf
